Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:41.32,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,That's hot! Ouchie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:44.65,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Calm down Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.99,0:01:51.95,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:02:01.22,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Help yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:05.43,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,She said 'Help yourselves' and looks very proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.76,0:02:07.80,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:09.25,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,I'm feeling chilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:10.94,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Cut it out. You're being creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.34,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:16.18,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,You can have the biggest one because you're a big guy Poppo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:17.15,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:20.68,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,She said you get it because you're the biggest one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:24.03,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.03,0:02:27.75,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,I've gotten really huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:32.41,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,It's good. It tastes really good Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:33.56,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.56,0:02:36.08,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,What about mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:38.71,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,What's mine going to have the most of?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:42.40,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yours will have the most raisins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:44.13,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I never said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:44.92,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:48.25,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I want you to tell me directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:51.53,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Please tell me Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:53.12,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:57.54,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! Let's see, here's some paper. And here's a pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:02:58.82,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Now Menma can show how she feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:03.29,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:06.05,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,What the? It doesn't work Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:08.54,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Why is that? You could write in the diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:10.04,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Let me try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:14.44,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,It looks like it still has ink in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:16.08,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Give it back! Let me try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:17.77,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:20.51,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Tsuruko that hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.94,0:03:22.83,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Tsuruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:30.15,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I feel really sleepy for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:33.59,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,I know what you mean. It's like I'm too relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:36.65,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:39.21,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Menma isn't angry at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:42.61,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,She forgave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:46.71,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,We don't know whether she's really forgiven us or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:52.33,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,What do you mean? I don't think she'd have made muffin bread for us if she was angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:58.06,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,It's also possible that she's appeared in order to condemn us precisely because she hasn't forgiven us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:01.37,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,That aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:06.25,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,If she could write all along, why didn't she just do that from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:12.04,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,You have a point there. If she did, we could have communicated with her and believed in her existence immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:15.43,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Both Menma and Jintan can be real airheads.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:16.34,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:20.05,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,He told us to believe in Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:22.46,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,But really he just wanted to keep her for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:26.84,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Hisakawa, Anjou, make sure to save up what you earn from your jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:28.08,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:30.03,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,We'll make fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:31.12,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:34.33,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I'll definitely make Menma go to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.35,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:46.19,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,You ran around in top gear for so long it's no wonder you're tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:52.90,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,We all want to make fireworks together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:54.02,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,To make you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.56,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Go to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:03.36,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Would you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:14.85,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,You were awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:16.47,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Thank you Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:20.59,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:28.28,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,It's fine like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:40.57,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:42.68,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:44.65,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:52.08,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Maybe it's really hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.46,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Round and round I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:56.05,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma! Running around like that is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:56.90,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:59.30,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Menma is running? Then I will too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.85,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Wait for me Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:04.00,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I'm over here Poppo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:04.00,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Well that's something. {I think she means something like "Well we kind of got left out." but doesn't finish the sentence}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:11.94,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,I couldn't forgive myself for liking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:15.77,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:16.41,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:17.35,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,That's the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:18.30,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:20.65,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,...can't give up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:25.78,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:30.84,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Could you cover my shift for next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:32.37,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Your shift?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:35.07,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,On Thursday they're doing construction on the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:37.71,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,The pay is high so I want to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:40.04,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.61,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,So she's finally gotten tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:44.49,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Hey, listen listen, over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:51.07,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:54.26,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You two are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:58.04,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Yeah, that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:01.69,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Meiko's mother probably told Yama about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:03.68,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,So it was her after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:08.04,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,So you're not the one against the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.61,0:07:16.91,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,She's still living in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:23.23,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Time hasn't moved at all for her since what happened to Meiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:27.60,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I want to pull her back into the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:32.41,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,That's why I don't want to force her to remember any more. Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:38.13,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.13,0:07:38.78,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:39.95,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Matsuyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:45.02,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I don't want to sound pretentious, but I think I understand how your wife feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:48.61,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I liked your daughter Meiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:52.51,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I want to do something for Meiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:57.82,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I was also living in the past, which is all the more reason I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:09.70,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,I was surprised you did something so uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:11.37,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I even surprised myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:13.94,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,You really haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:17.63,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,You'd do anything for Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:18.59,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Tsuruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:20.77,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Are you OK with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:21.60,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:26.03,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,If you really believe in Menma, are you okay with making her go to heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:32.07,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,You were so obsessed with Menma, and now you can even talk to her through Yadomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:32.99,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:34.96,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Only through Yadomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:37.69,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:39.99,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:42.62,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yo. What's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.84,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Are you heading to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:50.55,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll be working late tonight so I thought I'd take Menma home first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:54.19,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Is Menma here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:59.74,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,She doesn't want to be locked up inside so she's been following me everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:03.00,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Yeah. I want to try my best together with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:04.00,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:05.94,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,She says she wants to be together with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:12.92,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Is Menma's hair still long?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:14.65,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:20.45,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yeah. Actually she's grown like the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:22.20,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,She's grown?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.66,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I know right? I wonder why that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:27.99,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Is she hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.02,0:09:30.96,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:35.73,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Wh.. Who'd like an ugly girl like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:45.60,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,You know, so-so, sort of kind of hot... or rather, cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:47.99,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,What do you mean so-so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:48.84,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:50.58,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,You dumb dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:51.38,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Shut up stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:51.88,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,You idiot! You eggplant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:53.07,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,So-so is all you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:10:00.21,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,It's like a one-man theatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:05.29,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,But it's not like that. After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:12.03,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Yukiatsu has snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:24.06,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:26.26,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll let you make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:28.71,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:30.11,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Fireworks! Fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:32.97,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,We did it, we did it, we did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:35.96,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,I can't let you handle the combustible materials,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:38.09,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,but do you want to help out with the simple stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:38.32,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:41.46,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,We did it Jintan! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.88,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Please let us help out sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:50.84,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:52.67,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:58.80,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,That was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:10:59.93,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:04.03,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,So this thing comes out of the bamboo shoot right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:07.74,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,I think it would be cute with more red.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:12.65,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Cute? I honestly didn't think you had that side to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:17.08,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,And this is where you ignite it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:19.32,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I see. So how about this here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:21.86,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,That's just a decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:24.95,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,It makes it easier to carry when you take it to the launch pad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:27.27,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,That's super-awesomely awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:26.61,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,{\3c&H4E4E85&}And this is the same thing.  {timing check?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:29.25,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Super-awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.30,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Hey Jintan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:34.13,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Be careful Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:36.10,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Don't let go of that Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:37.84,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.83,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Are you done Poppo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:44.55,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,She just jumped onto your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:45.52,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:48.03,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Give me a break Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.03,0:11:50.96,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Poppopopo Poppo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:58.44,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Even though I can't see Menma, I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:01.84,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.94,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I can't measure up to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:07.86,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Not back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:09.07,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:10.20,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I can't measure up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:14.35,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:18.46,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,I'll go buy some juice or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:36.37,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:39.64,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,You saved me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:45.74,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,You ran away. I was about to start screaming back there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:46.97,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:51.03,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Menma is here with us. I've accepted that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:53.94,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,But I can't see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:56.30,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Nor can I talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:13:03.31,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I wanted to see her again. So why's it only Yadomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:04.90,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,It's all about Yadomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:09.68,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,And for Yadomi it's all about Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:11.86,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Nothing's changed since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:13.05,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Do you admit your defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:17.56,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,You were about to say 'Jintan' but immediately changed it to 'Yadomi'.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:22.65,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,What's with you and acting like you can see right through people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:24.88,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,You're the only one I can see through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:26.91,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Call it empathy between the like-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:30.98,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,I don't want to be compared to a freak like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:32.70,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Hey, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:43.04,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:52.24,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.14,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I said I was sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:11.42,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I was actually pretty serious about what I said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:13.08,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,What you said before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:15.86,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,About us going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:23.20,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,You're really not used to guys are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:24.98,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Don't pick on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:26.25,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Nice kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:30.87,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,What the hell do you mean 'nice kick'?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:32.42,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Stop laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:34.21,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,You really surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.63,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Is it really so surprising?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:39.81,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,That's the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:43.82,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm all fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:44.53,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:46.06,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Hey Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:48.70,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Anaru's stuffed animals aren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:51.21,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Did Anaru go back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:53.36,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Yeah, right out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:56.36,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,She's a stray little kitten, that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:15:03.88,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Say that Menma really is at your house, if you grant her wish, won't she disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:08.19,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,What's up Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:09.53,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:11.89,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Oh, it's time for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:13.30,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,You're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:14.34,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:15.61,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,How about you Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:17.19,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I'll stay with Poppo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:18.70,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,She says she wants to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:19.42,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Is that OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:21.98,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:26.86,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Of course it's fine. Stay right up in here yo. Really be up in here yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:29.81,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,You're making a ruckus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:31.74,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,That's because I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:39.49,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,She's happy right? I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:41.46,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.35,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Did you see that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:45.58,Default,Guy2,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:46.96,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,The one where the high school girl fights with nun-chucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:48.81,Default,Guy2,0,0,0,,So you've finally watched it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:53.45,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,{\3c&H4E4E85&}At first I thought of her as a beast of summer.  {timing check}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:57.76,Default,Guy2,0,0,0,,I bought the DVD and I heard there was a new one out too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:58.60,Default,Guy1,0,0,0,,A new one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:57.20,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,But now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.93,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I'm wearing winter clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:01.13,Default,Guy2,0,0,0,,A girl fights teachers with pom-poms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:03.15,Default,Guy2,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:10.79,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I can write!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:12.32,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Are you here Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:13.61,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:24.24,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Amazing. That's amazing Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:28.66,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,But I can't write on the paper at the house. I wonder why that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.66,0:16:31.76,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Write some more. Let's talk lots!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:37.80,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Well, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:43.52,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Back on that day. Did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:46.68,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.68,0:16:48.12,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Did you... me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:57.37,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I got it! Let's play shiritori! Shiritori with pictures! {http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shiritori so obviously it doesn't need a translation}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:58.82,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:00.44,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:05.25,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Hey what's that? It looks like a biscuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:08.19,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Sac.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:09.70,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:11.01,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Ra.. Ram.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:12.52,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Mario.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:15.08,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:20.47,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Take a hat in one hand and a pie in another, put them together, and you have 'happy!'
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:29.06,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Go binoculars!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:31.82,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Menma begins the investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:38.74,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Staaaaaaaare....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:50.20,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:01.39,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:06.71,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,The number you've dialed is currently...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:08.79,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Shit. It won't connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:09.81,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Is she at work already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:13.80,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Why am I walking more quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:19.30,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Why am I running?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:25.45,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma is probably at the secret base,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:31.97,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,so why am I like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:35.26,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:38.84,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Hey, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:42.05,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:44.93,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Jinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:48.64,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Menma has...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:58.17,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.87,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I don't want Menma to disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:07.78,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:25.26,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:28.99,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I don't want that to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:34.11,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I really, really don't want you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:38.75,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.79,0:19:41.79,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Aren't you dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:44.30,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.17,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,You're so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:52.43,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,The one who calls others weird is the weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:53.69,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:54.71,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:55.81,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:57.26,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Carp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:19:57.96,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Carp?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:01.43,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,There's a really big one in the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:05.25,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I wanted to see it up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:06.43,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:09.89,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,It's by those tree roots. It's all wavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:10.99,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:15.28,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.55,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:33.54,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,That hurts Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:36.00,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Do you need a hug? {Not sure how to TL this best, this is very far from literal}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.49,0:20:41.34,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Forever. Stay here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:44.63,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:48.72,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Stay... Stay here. I'll catch the carp for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:52.00,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,You'll get soaked Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.84,0:20:54.50,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:21:00.36,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Geez, are you stupid? You'll catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:17.72,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Come back here Jintan.
